{
	"_readme": "Low-drift retry of the direct d128/l3 entity-transformer arm. The 1e-4 v2 stage hit target-KL partway through epochs and regressed its direct screen from BC Elo 466 to gen5 Elo 456. This arm restarts from the untouched BC checkpoint, lowers LR to 3e-5, keeps two epochs/clip 0.1/KL guards, and disables per-generation distillation because strength is evaluated directly through the v2 socket.",
